    "body": "1. create genesis.json file \r\n```json\r\n{\r\n  \"config\": {\r\n    \"chainId\": 15,\r\n    \"homesteadBlock\": 0,\r\n    \"eip150Block\": 0,\r\n    \"eip155Block\": 0,\r\n    \"eip158Block\": 0,\r\n    \"byzantiumBlock\": 0,\r\n    \"constantinopleBlock\": 0,\r\n    \"petersburgBlock\": 0,\r\n    \"ethash\": {}\r\n  },\r\n  \"difficulty\": \"1\",\r\n  \"gasLimit\": \"8000000\",\r\n  \"alloc\": {\r\n    \"7df9a875a174b3bc565e6424a0050ebc1b2d1d82\": { \"balance\": \"300000\" },\r\n    \"f41c74c9ae680c1aa78f42e5647a62f353b7bdde\": { \"balance\": \"400000\" }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n```\r\n2.  run `geth --datadir data init genesis.json`\r\n```\r\nINFO [07-30|11:08:54.116] Maximum peer count                       ETH=50 LES=0 total=50\r\nINFO [07-30|11:08:54.118] Smartcard socket not found, disabling    err=\"stat /run/pcscd/pcscd.comm: no such file or directory\"\r\nINFO [07-30|11:08:54.121] Set global gas cap                       cap=50,000,000\r\nINFO [07-30|11:08:54.123] Allocated cache and file handles         database=/root/eth/dev/data/geth/chaindata cache=16.00MiB handles=16\r\nINFO [07-30|11:08:54.147] Opened ancient database                  database=/root/eth/dev/data/geth/chaindata/ancient readonly=false\r\nINFO [07-30|11:08:54.147] Writing custom genesis block \r\nINFO [07-30|11:08:54.147] Persisted trie from memory database      nodes=3 size=397.00B time=\"63.178µs\" gcnodes=0 gcsize=0.00B gctime=0s livenodes=1 livesize=0.00B\r\nINFO [07-30|11:08:54.148] Successfully wrote genesis state         database=chaindata                         hash=c3638c..f97051\r\nINFO [07-30|11:08:54.148] Allocated cache and file handles         database=/root/eth/dev/data/geth/lightchaindata cache=16.00MiB handles=16\r\nINFO [07-30|11:08:54.167] Opened ancient database                  database=/root/eth/dev/data/geth/lightchaindata/ancient readonly=false\r\nINFO [07-30|11:08:54.167] Writing custom genesis block \r\nINFO [07-30|11:08:54.168] Persisted trie from memory database      nodes=3 size=397.00B time=\"42.033µs\" gcnodes=0 gcsize=0.00B gctime=0s livenodes=1 livesize=0.00B\r\nINFO [07-30|11:08:54.168] Successfully wrote genesis state         database=lightchaindata                         hash=c3638c..f97051\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n3. run `geth --datadir data --networkid 15 --http --http.api personal,eth,net,miner,web3 --http.addr 0.0.0.0 --allow-insecure-unlock --rpc.allow-unprotected-txs console` \r\n\r\n```\r\n> personal.newAccount(\"123\")\r\n> miner.start(10)\r\n> eth.getBalance(eth.accounts[0])\r\n42000000000000000000\r\n> exit\r\n```\r\n4. Exit and restart \r\n```\r\n> eth.getBalance(eth.accounts[0])\r\n42000000000000000000\r\n\r\n```\r\n5. run with nohup `nohup geth --datadir data --networkid 15 --http --http.api personal,eth,net,miner,web3 --http.addr 0.0.0.0 --allow-insecure-unlock --rpc.allow-unprotected-txs     &` \r\n6. `cd data `\r\n7. `geth attach ipc:geth.ipc`\r\n```\r\n> eth.getBalance(eth.accounts[0])\r\n42000000000000000000\r\n\r\n```\r\n8. kill geth \r\n\r\n```\r\nps -ef | grep geth \r\nroot     14131 13983  2 11:12 pts/0    00:00:01 geth --datadir data --networkid 15 --http --http.api personal,eth,net,miner,web3 --http.addr 0.0.0.0 --allow-insecure-unlock --rpc.allow-unprotected-txs\r\nkill -9 14131 \r\n```\r\n9.  restart `nohup geth --datadir data --networkid 15 --http --http.api personal,eth,net,miner,web3 --http.addr 0.0.0.0 --allow-insecure-unlock --rpc.allow-unprotected-txs     &` \r\n10. `cd data `\r\n11. `geth attach ipc:geth.ipc`\r\n```\r\n> eth.getBalance(eth.accounts[0])\r\n42000000000000000000\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt's possible that after step 10 the data is zero",
